QuestData.Title: Moraya
QuestData.Description: Moraya has been lookin' for some help with tha raptors. Ya should talk to her on the other side of Darkspear Hold when ya get a chance.
QuestData.RewardText: Hey there, hon. Vol'jin sent you? So sweet of him to be thinkin' of me.$B$BI surely could use da help, but ya have a bit more walkin' ahead of ya.
